&quot;}]\">这个公众号历史发布过很多有趣的开源项目，如果你懒得翻文章一个个找，你直接和逛逛 GitHub 对话聊天就行了。</span></span></p>\n  <section data-mpa-preserve-tpl-color=\"t\" data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-preserve=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mvwie9lx8\">\n   <pre style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;line-height:2em;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:5.95px;white-space:nowrap;display:block;font-size:0.85em;overflow-x:auto;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mvwox96wq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"m9mvwox11oys\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mvwox1232s\">开源地址1：https://github.com/JefferyHcool/BiliNote</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">开源地址2：https://github.com/aehyok/video2blog</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">开源地址3：https://github.com/whotto/Video_note_generator</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9mvwox11r0u\">开源地址4：https://github.com/hanshuaikang/AI-Media2Doc</span></span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px 0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe js_wx_tap_highlight\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"逛逛GitHub\" 